Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個心情都興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  沒辦法維持啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這夏天給騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是小朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:54.49,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,600)\fad(500,500)}暑假哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳池哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！比基尼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是在充分享受夏天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來泳池啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就別玩那麼過火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快變成她們的監護人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能收斂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  柚子  小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緣你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…話說水到底是什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你問了我兩次…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水是…水就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  水是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然呆傳染了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一仔細琢磨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就變得難搞懂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  一時忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個惡劣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧  各種方面上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺小唯家像是有平常兩倍遠一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子  把夏天說十次看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:04:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天夏天夏天夏天夏天夏天夏天夏天夏天夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那金槍魚的英語是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tuna
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那說十次披薩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:18.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}和剛才夏天（natsu）和金槍魚（的段子一樣）\N這裡本是讓人說10遍披薩（piza）然後指著自己的手肘（hiji）問這是什麼\N一般人會反應不過來說膝蓋（hiza），結果柚子直接自己把這個遊戲全部完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手肘手肘手肘手肘手肘手肘手肘手肘手肘手肘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得讓你這麼累抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  很開心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  說十次披薩看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披薩披薩披薩披薩披薩披薩披薩披薩披薩披薩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手肘…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間裡好涼快  好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別聞我的枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  從今天開始就把這裡命名為天國
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從床上滾下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡要是天國的話那小唯就是天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使大人  請問這裡有冷飲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是個不要臉的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活過來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說今天城市裡會有40度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  難怪這麼熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十歲的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天四十歲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被無視了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無計劃亂說的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到件很厲害的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼  熱是一種能量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像卡路里什麼的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天不是很熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說周圍充滿了自然能量對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說超能力的力量會提升
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何止如此  說不定我們也會成為超能力者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼柚子你做點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於現在的我來說是沒有不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要怎麼發射出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹了空調也許就沒有夏天的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊對對  就是這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快給我滾回去  到外面好好發射去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  這種臨陣磨槍掌握的超能力和吹得到空調的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼事的話不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快滾回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊  你們還在那種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回家吧  天再暗下來就危險了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子：今天決定在小唯家過夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便決定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打開笨蛋  你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多內衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.50,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼啊  快開門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好意外哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然變安靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個沒救的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我挨揍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  柚子沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是  沒事的  打擾您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你媽媽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我吵到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦  那孩子平時很安靜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾吵鬧一下我也才放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺超羞人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼馬上換睡衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  你的睡衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近睡覺都穿T恤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:00.85,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:06.06,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這個夏天流行「如果不穿睡衣睡覺就會死亡」的病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕怕啊好怕怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這種病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿睡衣之前  小唯你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還很期待洗澡遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡衣和洗澡遊戲都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小唯  你有點汗臭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要口胡  這和睡衣是一個情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有汗臭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯有汗臭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗臭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  比剛才更有真實感了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那我們來講鬼故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一對夫妻的妻子死了以後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我打住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小唯同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼美妙的夜晚裡你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說沒有幽靈這種東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人這麼說過吧  幽靈的本體其實是可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的人還真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:12.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}原文是諺語「幽霊の正體見たり枯れ尾花」\N意為有對恐怖的懷疑心的話，平常的東西都會覺得恐怖。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是乾枯的芒草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說大家作業做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,700)}還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,700)}還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1050,700)}做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這幅表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  我開始變困了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不像是想睡的人的表情好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  必須睡啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須睡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我還要鋪被子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍你妹啊  滾下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我關燈了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  可以再來玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你們還會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠悠式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  請進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒跟柚子在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她說要考慮一個段子再來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要我不要說出來的事情被我給說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會說什麼樣的段子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是難懂的段子就糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是之前她一時流行的叫喊段子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  Dream什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的夢想是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢  是希望我們三人一直做好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  好安定的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了奇怪的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不行了  要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有5秒我就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託  最後再說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！  我就要死了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還專門找了潛水鏡再來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  讓我爸幫我找了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  緣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊啊  這個實在是太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼還要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我這邊都看的害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛才出賣了柚子  這是贖罪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小緣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊這是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你要來這套
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擺出那個表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才舔了那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎  是笨蛋嗎  你個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪子布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點說服力都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「幾經風霜」的發音真好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾經風霜  幾經風霜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.75,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的橡膠臭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  「臥薪嚐膽」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臥薪嚐膽  真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  總感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易拿來了就想要多用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不這麼勉強自己也可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一趟洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去清醒清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾你隨便用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會仰泳登場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事前預告？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來說一些全新的話題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看上這個了  這本書好像好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個的確很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了潛水夫的一本書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就買一本沒有潛水夫的書回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？那你隨便買本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  用心選購的書才能看得進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那個那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是野野原同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啊  為什麼我要躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本書  是我最喜歡的作者的新刊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得好認真的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到她還意外地喜歡看書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是可以志趣相投啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點震驚有點高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  震驚了什麼的  我真的好失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分  我真的好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搭個話比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把她嚇跑了就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這個  緣發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  南方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是特有的生物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上的特有的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緣還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海真美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是椰子樹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  緣的哥哥  好久沒見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張的小緣好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓢蟲？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帆船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左下角那片照糊了的  是蟲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這蟲出現的幾率…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是故意照的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想三個人一起去旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  想法不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去南方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想看冒出岩漿的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海中的空洞  那種也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的裂痕什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球肚臍之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的紗線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的某某
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  地球的正中是南極還是北極？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的世界的中心是小唯你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼的  三個人的時候那是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人的時候聽上去真的似的  還真是那什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是時候該回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要適當地挽留一下我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.02,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我差不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉  和你說重疊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是南方版啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天忘了塗防曬霜結果變成了這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那不是忘了而是嫌麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  緣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把頭髮弄傷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去了國外不可避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊  原本那麼漂亮的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆真親熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出500元  你倆繼續？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  給你們禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的點心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:18:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好沉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南方的度假地怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  你沒被蟲子怎麼樣吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？蟲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這個照片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中毒了  這下真的死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是死了的話長久以來真是對不起大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們拿點我的骨灰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  緣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得  對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小緣  死不了的死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得我死不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小緣是最強的  最強大的喲  最強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最強的  最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最強的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是市內最強…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狹隘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明剛從外國回來  卻好狹隘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我內心深處的矜持謙虛盡顯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謙虛的人會說自己謙虛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脖子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  好可愛好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛小唯  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看小唯可愛的一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自謙的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要道歉  倆笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要打脖子啊  這麼重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱點也叫做瓶頸的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緣就不要這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打脖子  這麼重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  柚子你已經不能說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全說不出話了啊
